Peterson
----------
Models peterson solution of mutual exclusion of concurent processes.
Modeled by Radek Pelanek.

peterson_bigerror.mdve -- model modified to contain quite a big error
			  (in particular, j:=j+1 changed to j:=j)

Parameters:
-----------
N=x -- the number of processes (defautl N=3)
ERROR=0,1 -- set ERROR to 1 to model an error in the protocol (default ERROR=0)
LOOPS=0,1 -- set LOOPS to 1 to allow each process to stay in critical section 
for an arbitrary number of steps (default LOOPS=0)
